cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.DS

This paper discusses the impact of the softmax function on the value function in reinforcement learning, which is a topic closely related to machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the convergence properties of the softmax Bellman operator, which is related to control systems and optimization, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category. Finally, the paper presents a comparison among different Bellman operators, which is related to data structures and algorithms, making cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) a possible category as well.
